Dependency Information

Apache Maven

<dependency>
  <groupId>org.getalp</groupId>
  <artifactId>dbnary</artifactId>
  <version>1.3-SNAPSHOT</version>
</dependency>

Apache Buildr

'org.getalp:dbnary:jar:1.3-SNAPSHOT'

Apache Ivy

<dependency org="org.getalp" name="dbnary" rev="1.3-SNAPSHOT">
  <artifact name="dbnary" type="jar" />
</dependency>

Groovy Grape

@Grapes(
@Grab(group='org.getalp', module='dbnary', version='1.3-SNAPSHOT')
)

Gradle/Grails

compile 'org.getalp:dbnary:1.3-SNAPSHOT'

Scala SBT

Leiningen
